T02D3548:184a-1: pradzny'a p'a ra mi t'a s'a dha nam /
T02D3548:184a-3: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin ma'i sgrub thabs /
T02D3548:184a-4: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3548:184a-6: bde ba'i stan la 'dug byas nas //
T02D3548:184a-7: rnal 'byor byams dang snying rjer ldan //
T02D3548:184a-8: sngags ni lan gsum brjod par bya //
T02D3548:184a-9: aom sh'u n+ya t'a dzny'a na badzra sva bh'a ba a'atma ko& ham /
T02D3548:184a-10: zhes pas brtan dang g-yo ba'i dngos //
T02D3548:184a-11: dag gi lus kyang thams cad du //
T02D3548:184a-12: sems kyis stong nyid bsgom par bya //
T02D3548:184a-13: rmi lam rmi lam mtshungs pa ru //
T02D3548:184a-14: pam yig rnam pa las skyes pa'i //
T02D3548:184a-15: padma zla ba'i gdan gnas pa'i //
T02D3548:184a-16: dh'i:yig ser po dgod bya ste //
T02D3548:184a-17: de yis bdag nyid bcom ldan ma //
T02D3548:184a-18: phyag gnyis shes rab pha rol phyin //
T02D3548:184a-19: sna tshogs gos 'chang sna tshogs rgyan//
T02D3548:184a-20: chos 'chad phyag rgya yang dag ldan //
T02D3548:184a-21: sgeg pa gcig pu'i nyams ldan zhing //
T02D3548:184a-22: rdo rje skyil krung yang dag gnas //
T02D3548:184a-23: pusti dang bcas chu skyes ni //
T02D3548:184a-24: g-yon gyi logs su bsnams pa'o //
T02D3548:184a-25: spyi bo mgrin pa snying gnas su //
T02D3548:184a-26: zla ba la gnas de nyid gsum //
T02D3548:184b-0: a'a:yig @184b h'um yig dag gi dbus //
T02D3548:184b-1: zla ba dhi:yig ser po yi //
T02D3548:184b-2: 'od zer rnam par bsgoms nas ni //
T02D3548:184b-3: de nas sku mdog ser mo bsgom //
T02D3548:184b-4: kun rdzob kyi ni rnal 'byor pas //
T02D3548:184b-5: shes rab shes rab bsgom par bya //
T02D3548:184b-6: don dam pa ni rtogs pa'i sku //
T02D3548:184b-7: shes rab bdag nyid chen por gsungs //
T02D3548:184b-8: gang gis byang chub nges thob pa'i //
T02D3548:184b-9: rim pa sbyor bas rgyal bar 'gyur //
T02D3548:184b-10: ston ka'i zla ba lta bu yi //
T02D3548:184b-11: dkar ba'i sems ni rnam par bsgom //
T02D3548:184b-12: sna tshogs g-yo dang mi g-yo ba //
T02D3548:184b-13: phyi nas nam mkha'i dpe dang 'dra //
T02D3548:184b-14: rnam rtog ma lus stong pa ste //
T02D3548:184b-15: rang byung stong pa gzugs kyang med //
T02D3548:184b-16: gzugs sgra dri dang ro dang ni //
T02D3548:184b-17: reg bya la sogs gzung dang 'dzin //
T02D3548:184b-18: rtog pas yongs su ma gos pa //
T02D3548:184b-19: bsam mi khyab pa'i rkyen las byung //
T02D3548:184b-20: yang dag rdzogs pa'i byang chub gnas //
T02D3548:184b-21: kun mkhyen sems kyi go 'phang ngo //
T02D3548:184b-22: de la bzlas pa'i sngags ni 'di'o //
T02D3548:184b-23: aom bradznye ma h'a pradznye shru ti smri ti bi dz'a ye dh'i:sv'a h'a /
T02D3548:184b-24: shes rab pha rol phyin bsgom pa'i //
T02D3548:184b-25: bdag byas bsod nams gang thob pa //
T02D3548:184b-26: de yis 'jig rten ma lus kun //
